.. Release. Civilization IV Warlords 12878 UBCrack Upgrade for MAC OS X 10.5.
.. Format.  Fuck
.. Install. 
    +1 We assume you installed Civilization IV already.
    +2 Install Civilization IV Warlords.
    +3 Take the "Civilization IV Warlords" Application here and replace it with
        the one that was just installed. Be careful not to put it in the same
        place as the alias, as this will not work. The proper location should be
        in something like Civilization IV/Warlords/.
    +4 You can play now.

.. Notes. 
    Just in case that doesn't work, we have the original UBCrack patcher with a
    supposed Leopard update. Since the first Crack we have works perfectly fine,
    we never tested this, but in theory it should work.

.. Greetz.
    to THE BLADE CORPORATION for cracking this fucking great game.
